Extract simulation layer outputs

Source: R/meta--layer-extractors.R
get_layer_output.Rd

Extracts the output data.frame of a erahumed_simulation_layer.

Usage

get_layer_output(object, ...)

# S3 method for class 'erahumed_simulation_layer'
get_layer_output(object, ...)

# S3 method for class 'erahumed_simulation'
get_layer_output(object, layer, ...)

Arguments

object

The object from which the layer output is to be extracted from (see above for available methods).

...

further arguments passed to or from other methods.

layer

A string. Name of the layer whose output data.frame is to be extracted.

Value

A data.frame.
